<tr class="odd">
<td>Search Engine Optimization</td>
<td>Enablement</td>
<td></td>
<td>EQUATOR’s website did not make use of some commonly used search optimization heuristics. It ranked well for guideline acronyms (like STROBE) but not for general terms that naive authors may use, like “observational epidemiology”.</td>
<td>Site has meta data required by search engines</td>
</tr>
