<td>Permanent links (DOIs)</td>
<td>Enablement</td>
<td></td>
<td>Although guideline publications have DOIs, tools (commonly hosted on guideline developer’s websites) do not. EQUATOR’s website does not use document object identifiers. If resources move (e.g. a website is reorganised or depreciated) then links can “die”.</td>
<td>No change</td>
</tr>
